hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191101/mobile/bkn-20191101111347018-1101_00822_001.html</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:40:44.000Z","msg":"告佢性騷擾毛EE, 食洋腸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:43:34.000Z","msg":"但係議事廳內一切言論受到權力特權法保護，應該告唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:06:28.000Z","msg":"咁喺議事廳內講佢有黑社會嫌疑都冇事啦<br />\n咁係咪次次同何XX講「屌你老母」再收回？"},{"pid":"15d7cd8501093b4dac6915b604a902bd389beaae","tid":1686192,"uid":22617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:07:43.000Z","msg":"咁你咪證明自己唔係囉 證明到話你英雄 唔係就豬雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41442fc2cab3c6c85b11306059e5c083d518a469","tid":1686192,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:08:28.000Z","msg":"黑社會何君堯"},{"pid":"f620999b12bd8b91c835e5a6c28d49aa1ce328f8","tid":1686192,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"要調查下佢係唔係黑先有得話誹謗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75168e715ce8416ef11129398dbfb01063c2281","tid":1686192,"uid":35365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:08:57.000Z","msg":"誹謗首先要講完令人地因此相信而導致你有損失<br />\n但撐你既聽完唔會信<br />\n反你既一早知你同班鄉黑有關唔駛靠毛ee佢地講<br />\n所以點會告得入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46438f204929e4e135292af46145da760ce0285","tid":1686192,"uid":279981,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eab236065c2d23a651b4000e367a6f2f69ed211c","tid":1686192,"uid":195084,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"654be01d97e4bf2e5f9f0ae6ead2373d54500826","tid":1686192,"uid":279981,"like":13,"dislike":10,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b28df7b79adcc0ac7dbc03082d7bc9ce25566481","tid":1686192,"uid":8441,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:42:41.000Z","msg":"立法會入面講免責<br />